Valuation Inc. is a financial technology company seeking to create the world's first AI investment manager capable of autonomous fundamental equity valuation and investment management (linkedin.com/company/valuation-inc/). We are currently valued between $10-$15 million by the top VC fund in Berkeley.

Our company is currently looking for CTO with a strong background in full-stack development. If you are passionate about the application of AI in fundamental equity investing, please reach out to Boris by email: boriswang@mba.berkeley.edu or by linkedin: linkedin.com/in/boris-wang/.
history.subject: Posting for a friend: Berkeley Startup looking for a CTO
